('05a53442-4dbb-4b65-8c82-c2c13cee07a6', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Yoga-classes for refugees', 'Yoga-classes for refugees at the Prana Yoga Zentrum, Schönfelder Str. 12 (DD-Neustadt) for a maximum  of 12  participants - or at other locations, close to the refugee accommodations, in case there is something suitable to find.\r\nThe classes could take place during the following times:\r\n- Mo. 11:00 - 15:00\r\n- Wed. 12:00 - 15:00\r\n- Fr. 14:00-16:00\r\n- Sa. 13:00-15:00', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 1, '', '5614fc6fec832', 'en', '2015-10-23 07:53:17', '2016-06-21 17:23:02', 0, NULL, NULL),
('05e10f70-51c4-4dfc-8cd4-aa3346fb494e', '92276b73-dca7-4e8f-958c-999ca8ced377', 'adfb2457-819c-4574-ace1-56f5b38d8f96', NULL, '2017-03-31', '', '14:00', '17:15', 'dresden', 'Perspektivwechsel. Ein interkulturelles Sensibilisierungstraining', 'Sie möchten die Fähigkeit erlangen, in interkulturellen Situationen angemessen und konfliktvermeidend zu interagieren. Mit diesem interkulturellen Sensibilisierungstraining bekommen Sie die Möglichkeit, sich mit Ihrer eigenen kulturellen Prägung auseinanderzusetzen und Normalitätskonstruktionen der deutschen Kultur zu hinterfragen und zu verstehen. Ziel des Seminars ist es, interkulturelle Konfliktpotentiale in der Kommunikation zu erkennen und vermeiden zu lernen.\r\n\r\n1 x | 4 UE | gebührenfrei\r\n17F 44106\r\nFr, 31.03., 14.00 – 17.15 Uhr', '', '', '', '', 'lecture', 2, '', '', '', '', 0, 0, '', 1, NULL, '58b04b75dec34', 'de', '2017-02-24 16:04:21', '2017-02-24 16:04:21', 0, NULL, NULL),
('05f78683-5497-4392-bfda-87bd3de08927', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Clothes shop of the Salvation Army/Heilsarmee', 'The clothes shop "Zweite Chance", or Second Chance, offers all customers the option to get used clothing, household appliances and books, as well "junk" to buy. To get free clothes you must have an "in-need" document (ALG II proof, Dresdenpass/Dresden passport for citizens of Dresden or corresponding pension notification).\r\n\r\nWe also welcome donations of clothes!\r\n\r\nThe small coffee corner invites you to the community and to talk to each other.\r\n\r\n The store is located at the Heilsarmee/Salvation Army around the corner - Keplerstraße. 4', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 1, '', '5570b8db255b3', 'en', '2015-11-29 21:15:57', '2016-06-21 17:23:01', 0, NULL, NULL),
