('0e4f46a6-aec5-4096-ba2f-ee7dc25f44f7', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', NULL, 'All over the world people are fleeing more than ever before. The reasons for leaving their home are diverse and complex - just as the global entanglements, which cause the crises, from which people flee.\r\n\r\nIn this seminar we focus at first on the causes on a global scale and the migration movements towards Europe and Germany. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '574c39d71c395', 'en', '2016-09-02 11:37:08', '2016-09-02 11:37:08', 0, NULL, NULL);
