('1a102361-7eb0-4a85-a3d1-f3547a467f23', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Donations Collection Center "Willkommen in Löbtau"', 'There is a collecting and giveaway of donations in the backroom of Emil-Überall street 6.\r\n\r\nWhat donations we currently need is found under:\r\nhttps://www.dresden.de/media/pdf/sozialamt/asyl/wil_spendenaufruf_08-2016.pdf\r\n\r\nThe donations room is open for all refugees and is also a meeting place for refugees and the citizens of Löbtau. Therefore we use the room to introduce other offers from our networks and initiatives and we answer different kinds of questions. It''s also possible, during our opening times, to bring and attach notices on the bulletin board.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '559252adbc796', 'en', '2017-02-21 23:30:03', '2017-02-21 23:30:03', 0, '"Willkommen in Löbtau", in the Emil-Überall-Straße 6, offers a collecting place to gather donations for refugees. The collecting place is also used as a meeting point.', NULL),
