('29205b44-60e9-4166-9983-ea492e0c91bd', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Café International in Artderkultur e.V.', 'The Café International is a place to get to know asylum seekers, locals, migrants... and is organized by a group of asylum seekers, locals, migrants...\r\n\r\nCafé International homework support:\r\nhomework support/tutoring in maths, physics, ethics history, chemistry, geography, English and German. Every Friday 15-18 at veränderbar. Everyone is welcomed to join. \r\nNo enrollment necessary \r\nContact: joni.cafeint@gmail.com\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '556e1d2e344e8', 'en', '2016-11-22 15:30:42', '2016-11-22 15:30:42', 0, 'The Café International is a meeting point for asylum seekers, locals, migrants... and is organized by a group of asylum seekers, locals, migrants... We also offer homework support (see below).', NULL),
