('373186c4-0f8a-4d95-82bd-bd8f99a0966f', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', NULL, '"Gorbitz plays with us" is an open mobile playground offer for kids between 6 and 12 by the Ausländerrat in Dresden, with the cooperation of the Wirbelwind der Outlaw gGmbH. Every Tuesday  we go to a park between Altgorbitzer and Wölfnitzer Ring with a lot of toys and ideas for exploring and discovering games in the area. \r\nOnce a month there''s an Outdoor cooking activity, where we bring cooking tools, pots and everything else for cooking. We want to cook a lot of international food with the kids, and eat them together.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '575ff35bd5ac0', 'en', '2017-02-21 23:30:07', '2017-02-21 23:30:07', 0, NULL, NULL),
