('7f4fb7a1-1f1e-4881-9c96-dd71166585ce', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'كاريتاس درسدن - Caritasverband für Dresden e.V.', 'ونحن نقدم المساعدة والمشورة في المجالات التالية:\r\n\r\n خدمة هجرة الشباب\r\n نبلغ، ونقدم المشورة ودعم الشباب من أصول مهاجرة: الأطفال والشباب تحت 27 وأسرهم. نحن هناك لك إذا كان لديك أسئلة أو بحاجة إلى مساعدة.\r\n\r\n الخدمات الاستشارية الأولية للمهاجرين\r\n المشورة للأجانب الذين يعيشون في ألمانيا، واللاجئين، (الراحل) العائدين والمهاجرين اليهود، من مواطني الاتحاد الأوروبي وأسرهم.\r\n\r\nعمل اجتماعي اللاجئين\r\n لقد كان العملمع طالبي اللجوء واللاجئين وغيرهم من المهاجرينعلى المدى الطويل جزءا لا يتجزأ من عرض المساعدات في كاريتاس.\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '557ac3ba0cf23', 'ar', '2017-03-20 14:01:01', '2017-03-20 14:01:01', 0, NULL, NULL),
('7f55a01a-7b7d-4da1-9fe8-38296a3a8e04', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Presentation of the study "Split Middle" and subsequent panel discussion', 'The "Friedrich-Ebert-Foundation (FES)" invites you to a presentation for the FES-Study "Split Middle. Hostile States. Extreme Right wing attitudes in Germany 2016" and a subsequent discussion panel.\r\nOur speakers:\r\n- Dr. Ralf Melzer, the publisher of the Study for the FES, working branch "Against right-wing extremism"\r\n- Henning Homann, MdL, Deputy Chairman of the SPD faction, speaker of the democratic culture\r\n- Dr. Christian Demuth, an advisory board member of the "Sachsen-Monitor"\r\nThe moderation will be done by Grit Hanneforth, director of the Cultural Office of Saxony e.V.\r\n\r\nRegistration over our website is possible.\r\n\r\nDownloadbale study: \r\nhttp://www.fes-gegen-rechtsextremismus.de/pdf_16/Gespaltene%20Mitte_Feindselige%20Zust%C3%A4nde.pdf', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '58aca6fd1f9b3', 'en', '2017-03-20 14:01:30', '2017-03-20 14:01:30', 0, NULL, NULL),
('7f641d68-85d9-4ee5-97eb-570d42d20961', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'First Kurdish film days in Dresden', 'Wanted: Interested school classes for film meetings on the 3rd of March!\r\n\r\nThe association UTA e.V. Frauenrat, an emancipating foundation of women from the Kurdish community,  organize mainly these events.\r\n\r\nWe''re looking for help on the 3rd of March in organizing applications of conceptual events, which are directed towards school girls for the most part. School classes (starting from the 7th class) can register for the 3 presentations, which happen at 10 am, 1 pm and 4 pm. The interesting part about those presentations is that the protagonists of the film "The Beekeeper" Ibrahim Gezer (Who is a documented beekeeper who talks about his refuge and migration story) and the director Manou Khalil will talk directly to the school girls.\r\n\r\nFor more information about the film "The Beekeeper:\r\nhttp://film-kultur.de/glob/der-imker_kc.pdf', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '58acad4a7d2be', 'en', '2017-03-20 14:01:30', '2017-03-20 14:01:30', 0, NULL, NULL),
