('85f5261f-dc77-43ac-9053-15f094f95c92', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'International Gardens Dresden e. V.', 'The goal of this organization is to establish a community garden in Dresden in which people from different countries can grow fruits and vegetables together, get to know each other, and share. "Internationalen Gärten Dresden" wants to provide space for taking initiative, self-organization, and exchanging knowledge. We are a place for meeting, communicating, and producing. Those involved in the garden can contribute to their self-sufficiency, get to know people from other countries, make their ideas come true, and develop intercultural expertise. \r\nNext to gardening we also provide space for education and cultural and social events.  \r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '556e1d2cc160c', 'en', '2017-02-21 23:30:00', '2017-02-21 23:30:00', 0, 'The goal of the association is to establish a community garden in which people from different countries of origin can equally grow fruits and vegetables together while getting to know each other and share.', NULL),
