('a554238f-b386-45dc-b15f-60070684732f', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'HATiKVA e.V.', 'مركز التعليم و اللقاء للتاريخ والحضارة اليهودية في ساكسونيا يعمل منذ تأسيسه على نشر الثقافة و التاريخ اليهودي. دام بناء المركز سنتين بعد عمل مكثف من قبل متطوعين, و بعد ذلك فتحت غرفه في الـ Genossenschaftshauses Pulsnitzer Str. 10 في درسدن للعامة.\r\nو منذ حين تطورت الـ HATiKVA e.V. الى واحدة من اكثر المراكز ذات تأثير في نشر التعليم والحضارة المرتبط بتخصصه, و وصل هذا التأثير حتى خارج درسدن. من أحد مواضيعه الرئيسة هو "تعليم الاطفال والشباب خارج المدرسة", الذي هو فريد من نوعه في مقاطعة ساكسونيا.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '5652df61e410f', 'ar', '2017-03-20 14:01:07', '2017-03-20 14:01:07', 0, NULL, NULL),
('a56069f7-6e45-41e6-85c7-b474dbb9176b', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The book&movie-club', 'The book&movie-club is for children and young teenagers who like to read and watch movies. Every saturday we meet at the Casablanca and either read a book or watch the film version of the book. All the books are classic german children books. We have a list of books and you can always choose the next one we will be reading. \nThe event is free of charge and every saturday from 10am to 12pm. Please let us know if you‘re coming so we can estimate the number of guests. Write a quick e-mail to anne@casablanca-dresden.de.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '570fabedf21f4', 'en', '2016-04-15 13:14:24', '2016-06-21 17:23:03', 0, NULL, NULL),
('a56f9817-a160-4631-afe0-ee20b62a2ff3', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Malika - Support for Refugee Women', 'We''re currently looking for help in:\r\n-        Teaching German courses\r\n-        Child care during the courses\r\n-        For our Orgateam\r\nNo qualifications needed, but interest in meeting new people is required', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '57fa86880b38e', 'en', '2017-02-21 23:30:09', '2017-02-21 23:30:09', 0, 'We are a group of women #Frauen that stands up for the concerns and needs of female refugees in Dresden. We offer our support through basic German language courses and cultural projects with different organizations.  \r\n\r\nWe''re also looking for help. (check below)', NULL),
