('a8dd59ea-0b71-4a04-853c-4ea23fed2f4c', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'German Courses in SPIKE Dresden', 'In our facilities, volunteers offer German courses for refugees. There are two formats – a “classic” German class and a computerised learning programme with individual support (SPEAK). Both offers especially address people who are currently not having access to regular integration courses/German offers. We cannot provide a certificate or diploma.\r\n\r\nGerman with teacher\r\nMon. - Thurs. 3pm - 5pm\r\n\r\nSPEAK Project with laptop\r\nTues. - Thurs. 5pm-7pm', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 1, '', '556e1d3a0df7c', 'en', '2015-06-02 23:17:29', '2016-06-21 17:23:01', 0, 'Voluntary helpers offer German courses for refugees in our offices. We provide two different formats: the "classic" German course and a computer aided one with individual support (SPEAK).', NULL),
