('b5e152aa-7537-4387-a9f8-c045ac3e61d5', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Prohlis is colourful', 'The network "Prohlis ist bunt" ("Prohlis is colourful") is a union of clubs, institutions, the city district bureau, quarter management, church association and parties in Prohlis and aims to create a welcoming atmosphere in this region. Main tasks are the networking and the project activities. The network exists since spring 2014.\r\n\r\nThe network invites refugees every last sunday of the month between 10 and 12 to meet each other and to do something together.', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', 0, NULL, NULL, 1, '', '556e1d2c45abc', 'en', '2015-06-02 23:16:49', '2016-06-21 17:23:01', 0, 'The network „Prohlis ist bunt“ wants to create a welcoming climate for asylum seekers and refugees in Prohlis. The network invites refugees and everyone who is interested every last Sunday of the month from 10am-12pm to meet and do something together.', NULL),
