('bf31e382-4607-4866-ae6d-ff2c90492312', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Ausländerrat e.V. - Intercultural women''s get-together', 'It is the objective of our work to support women with or without migrant background on their realisation of their claims for a fulfilled life – according to their measure –, an independent securing of their livelihood and a personal development.\r\nThe work of our project is an important contribution towards gender equality. It offers women a protected atmosphere for further education and strengthening their personality. We support women on living self-determined and independent and on more and more demanding this.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '578f772179d9e', 'en', '2016-09-18 19:24:26', '2016-09-18 19:24:26', 0, 'Our project offers #women a protected space to further develop and strengthen their personalities. We support women in obtaining a self-determined and independent life and the ability to stand up for it.\r\n\r\n#Frauen', NULL),
