('ca15890a-145a-40cc-8a6f-dc48ee936a53', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Ausländerrat Dresden e.V.- IBZ International Meeting Center (IBZ)', 'Are you a migrant and have problems with offices, your landlord or your employer? Did you recieve a letter that you cannot understand, or do not know how to respond? \r\nOur counselling  office might be able to assist you. We try to help, and if we cannot achieve that we will show you who else to consult. ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '578f66eae1d0b', 'en', '2017-02-21 23:30:07', '2017-02-21 23:30:07', 0, 'The ''Ausländerrat Dresden e.V.'' supports everyone from a migration background in Dresden. Our goal is to support cultural, social, and political integration of migrants and to strengthen their self-representation.', NULL),
