('d1b35f5e-3221-428a-afe9-3c3b64f9b5f7', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'KulturLoge Dresden', 'The ''KulturLoge Dresden'' makes it possible for refugees and people with low incomes to have access to cultural and sport event.  \r\n\r\nUsually, the events are attanded together with a voluntary companion or mentor as a pair or as a group. The tickets will be picked up right at the ticket office of the event. Whether a game of ''Dynamo Dresden'' or ''Dresdner Eislöwen'', or an event in the ''Scheune'' or ''Staatsoperette'' - Kulturloge always has the right offers. To recieve tickets for an event together with one or a group of refugees, please contact KulturLoge.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '55786558b9c07', 'en', '2017-03-20 14:01:17', '2017-03-20 14:01:17', 0, NULL, NULL),
